Salesforce Commerce Object Permissions

When you enable object and field permissions for Salesforce Commerce objects, object names can differ under the connector integration permission sets.

The table maps the Salesforce Commerce objects to the object name for permission sets. For objects that depend on another object, you can set only field-level permissions. For example, the ReturnOrderProductAdjustment object depends on ReturnOrder.

Salesforce Commerce object names are linked to data source object mappings.

Coupon	Coupons	
FulfillmentOrder	Fulfillment Orders	
FulfillmentOrderProduct	Fulfillment Order Products	
FulfillmentOrderProductPriceAdjustment	Fulfillment Order Item Adjustments

OrderDeliveryMethod	Order Delivery Methods

ProcessException	Process Exceptions

Promotion	Promotions

ReturnOrderProductTax	Return Order Item Taxes
